2. 基础设施层 (engine-infrastructure) - 完整实现

现在，我们来提供基础设施层中这三个核心类的完整代码。

configuration/ConfigurationManager.java

这个类是运行时配置定义的核心管理者。它实现了两个仓储接口，并统一管理来自所有配置提供者的定义缓存。

Java
package com.example.engine.infrastructure.configuration;

import com.example.engine.domain.aggregate.ProcessDefinition;
import com.example.engine.domain.aggregate.RuleChainDefinition;
import com.example.engine.domain.primitive.ProcessDefinitionId;
import com.example.engine.domain.primitive.RuleChainId;
import com.example.engine.domain.repository.ProcessDefinitionRepository;
import com.example.engine.domain.repository.RuleChainDefinitionRepository;
import com.example.engine.domain.spi.ProcessDefinitionProvider;
import com.example.engine.domain.spi.RuleChainDefinitionProvider;
import jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;
import org.slf4j.Logger;
import org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;
import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;

import java.util.Collection;
import java.util.List;
import java.util.Map;
import java.util.Optional;
import java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap;
import java.util.function.Function;
import java.util.stream.Collectors;

/**
 * 配置定义管理器（完整实现）
 * <p>
 * 1. 作为运行时定义缓存的持有者。
 * 2. 实现两个仓储接口，为领域服务提供统一的、基于缓存的定义访问点。
 * 3. 协调所有配置提供者（YAML, DB等）来加载和刷新定义。
 */
@Component
public class ConfigurationManager implements ProcessDefinitionRepository, RuleChainDefinitionRepository {

    private static final Logger log = LoggerFactory.getLogger(ConfigurationManager.class);

    private final Map<ProcessDefinitionId, ProcessDefinition> processCache = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();
    private final Map<RuleChainId, RuleChainDefinition> ruleChainCache = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();

    private final List<ProcessDefinitionProvider> processProviders;
    private final List<RuleChainDefinitionProvider> ruleChainProviders;

    public ConfigurationManager(List<ProcessDefinitionProvider> processProviders,
                                List<RuleChainDefinitionProvider> ruleChainProviders) {
        this.processProviders = processProviders;
        this.ruleChainProviders = ruleChainProviders;
    }

    @PostConstruct
    public void initialize() {
        log.info("Initializing definition caches...");
        refreshProcesses();
        refreshRuleChains();
    }

    /**
     * 独立刷新流程定义缓存。
     */
    public void refreshProcesses() {
        log.info("Refreshing process definitions cache from all providers...");
        Map<ProcessDefinitionId, ProcessDefinition> newDefinitions = processProviders.stream()
                .peek(provider -> log.info("Loading processes from source: {}", provider.getSourceName()))
                .flatMap(provider -> provider.loadProcessDefinitions().stream())
                .collect(Collectors.toMap(
                        ProcessDefinition::id,
                        Function.identity(),
                        (existing, replacement) -> {
                            log.warn("Duplicate ProcessDefinitionId found: {}. The definition from a later provider will overwrite the existing one.", existing.id());
                            return replacement;
                        }
                ));

        processCache.clear();
        processCache.putAll(newDefinitions);
        log.info("Process definitions cache refreshed. Total loaded: {}", processCache.size());
    }

    /**
     * 独立刷新规则链定义缓存。
     */
    public void refreshRuleChains() {
        log.info("Refreshing rule chain definitions cache from all providers...");
        Map<RuleChainId, RuleChainDefinition> newDefinitions = ruleChainProviders.stream()
                .peek(provider -> log.info("Loading rule chains from source: {}", provider.getSourceName()))
                .flatMap(provider -> provider.loadRuleChainDefinitions().stream())
                .collect(Collectors.toMap(
                        RuleChainDefinition::id,
                        Function.identity(),
                        (existing, replacement) -> {
                            log.warn("Duplicate RuleChainId found: {}. The definition from a later provider will overwrite the existing one.", existing.id());
                            return replacement;
                        }
                ));
        ruleChainCache.clear();
        ruleChainCache.putAll(newDefinitions);
        log.info("Rule chain definitions cache refreshed. Total loaded: {}", ruleChainCache.size());
    }

    // --- ProcessDefinitionRepository 实现 ---
    @Override
    public Optional<ProcessDefinition> findById(ProcessDefinitionId id) {
        return Optional.ofNullable(processCache.get(id));
    }

    @Override
    public Collection<ProcessDefinition> findAll() {
        return processCache.values();
    }

    @Override
    public ProcessDefinition save(ProcessDefinition aggregateRoot) {
        processCache.put(aggregateRoot.id(), aggregateRoot);
        log.info("Process definition {} saved/updated in cache.", aggregateRoot.id());
        // 注意：这只更新了缓存。如果需要持久化到DB，需要一个专门的DB写入服务。
        return aggregateRoot;
    }

    @Override
    public void delete(ProcessDefinition aggregateRoot) {
        deleteById(aggregateRoot.id());
    }

    @Override
    public void deleteById(ProcessDefinitionId id) {
        processCache.remove(id);
        log.info("Process definition {} deleted from cache.", id);
    }

    // --- RuleChainDefinitionRepository 实现 ---
    @Override
    public Optional<RuleChainDefinition> findById(RuleChainId id) {
        return Optional.ofNullable(ruleChainCache.get(id));
    }

    @Override
    public Collection<RuleChainDefinition> findAll() {
        return ruleChainCache.values();
    }

    @Override
    public RuleChainDefinition save(RuleChainDefinition aggregateRoot) {
        ruleChainCache.put(aggregateRoot.id(), aggregateRoot);
        log.info("Rule chain definition {} saved/updated in cache.", aggregateRoot.id());
        return aggregateRoot;
    }

    @Override
    public void delete(RuleChainDefinition aggregateRoot) {
        deleteById(aggregateRoot.id());
    }

    @Override
    public void deleteById(RuleChainId id) {
        ruleChainCache.remove(id);
        log.info("Rule chain definition {} deleted from cache.", id);
    }
}

configuration/yaml/YamlProcessDefinitionProvider.java

这个类负责从指定的YAML文件路径加载 ProcessDefinition。

Java
package com.example.engine.infrastructure.configuration.yaml;

import com.example.engine.domain.aggregate.ProcessDefinition;
import com.example.engine.domain.spi.ProcessDefinitionProvider;
import org.slf4j.Logger;
import org.slf4j.LoggerFactory;
import org.springframework.beans.factory.annotation.Value;
import org.springframework.core.io.Resource;
import org.springframework.core.io.support.PathMatchingResourcePatternResolver;
import org.springframework.stereotype.Component;
import org.yaml.snakeyaml.Yaml;

import java.io.InputStream;
import java.util.ArrayList;
import java.util.Collection;
import java.util.Collections;
import java.util.List;
import java.util.Map;

/**
 * 从YAML文件加载流程定义的提供者（完整实现）。
 */
@Component
public class YamlProcessDefinitionProvider implements ProcessDefinitionProvider {
    private static final Logger log = LoggerFactory.getLogger(YamlProcessDefinitionProvider.class);

    private final String location;
    private final YamlDefinitionMapper mapper;
    private final Yaml yaml = new Yaml();

    public YamlProcessDefinitionProvider(
            @Value("${process-engine.config.sources.yaml.process-location:}") String location,
            YamlDefinitionMapper mapper) {
        this.location = location;
        this.mapper = mapper;
    }
    
    @Override
    public Collection<ProcessDefinition> loadProcessDefinitions() {
        if (location == null || location.isBlank()) {
            log.warn("YAML process definition location is not configured. Skipping loading.");
            return Collections.emptyList();
        }

        log.info("Loading process definitions from YAML location: {}", location);
        List<ProcessDefinition> definitions = new ArrayList<>();
        try {
            Resource[] resources = new PathMatchingResourcePatternResolver().getResources(location);
            for (Resource resource : resources) {
                log.debug("Parsing process definition from file: {}", resource.getFilename());
                try (InputStream inputStream = resource.getInputStream()) {
                    Map<String, Object> data = yaml.load(inputStream);
                    // YAML文件可能为空或者被注释掉
                    if (data != null && !data.isEmpty()) {
                        definitions.add(mapper.toProcessDefinition(data));
                    }
                } catch (Exception e) {
                    log.error("Failed to parse YAML file: {}", resource.getFilename(), e);
                    // 选择继续加载其他文件，而不是让整个过程失败
                }
            }
        } catch (Exception e) {
            log.error("Failed to resolve resources from location pattern: {}", location, e);
            // 这种情况下通常是配置错误，可以选择抛出异常使应用启动失败
            throw new RuntimeException("Could not load process definitions from " + location, e);
        }
        log.info("Loaded {} process definitions from YAML files.", definitions.size());
        return definitions;
    }

    @Override
    public String getSourceName() {
        return "YAML-Processes";
    }
}
